    },
    {
      "start": 13.86,
      "end": 16.36,
      "text": "Yeah, the director, 미아 한순 러브."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.94,
      "end": 21.6,
      "text": "Most of her movies, she says, are based on her own life, life stories."
    },
    {
      "start": 22.06,
      "end": 24.22,
      "text": "And it's very interesting."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.52,
      "end": 28.06,
      "text": "맞아요. 그래서 어떤 인터뷰에서 she said this."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.06,
      "end": 29.3,
      "text": "이렇게 이야기했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 29.48,
      "end": 33.98,
      "text": "Honestly, I wish I could make films less connected to myself."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.98,
      "end": 35.02,
      "text": "Less connected."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.38,
      "end": 38.72,
      "text": "So she wants to stop making films about herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.98,
      "end": 39.92,
      "text": "But it's not easy."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.14,
      "end": 40.8,
      "text": "Not easy."
    },
    {
      "start": 40.96,
      "end": 42.54,
      "text": "Why does she keep making movies?"
