    {
      "start": 42.7,
      "end": 43.12,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.12,
      "end": 44.04,
      "text": "She could just stop it."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.88,
      "end": 48.32,
      "text": "아무래도 영화이든지 아니면 책이든지"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.32,
      "end": 52.42,
      "text": "자신의 인생을 반영을 할 수밖에 없는 장르인 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.92,
      "end": 55.98,
      "text": "And actually, she has a 좀 사연이 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.14,
      "end": 60.12,
      "text": "She has a particular reason for making movies about herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.12,
      "end": 64.02,
      "text": "She says she has a very, very, very bad memory."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.42,
      "end": 65.44,
      "text": "Terrible memory."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.56,
      "end": 66.2,
      "text": "아, 진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.3,
      "end": 66.58,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 67.5,
      "end": 73.34,
      "text": "So she wants to hold on to events that, so she can remember events in her own life."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.4,
      "end": 75.62,
      "text": "And she does this by making movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.72,
      "end": 78.44,
      "text": "And the movies reflect her own life."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.44,
      "end": 82.14,
      "text": "So she won't forget those precious or interesting moments."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.28,
      "end": 88.98,
      "text": "와, 자신의 기억력이 좀 안 좋아가지고 기억을 하기 위해서 이렇게 영화화하는 거네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.24,
      "end": 92.46,
      "text": "Yeah, she says I'm always worried that I'll forget everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 92.62,
      "end": 92.94,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.22,
      "end": 95.18,
      "text": "And I make movies, so I will remember."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.18,
      "end": 100.9,
      "text": "I would never have expected that reason, but I can identify with that."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.9,
      "end": 110.18,
      "text": "음, 설명을 들으면 이해가 되기는 한데, 근데 인터뷰에서는 I wish I could make films less connected to myself 라고 이야기를 했는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.56,
      "end": 113.04,
      "text": "어, 여건 좀 앞뒤가 안 맞는 건 아닌가 싶기도 하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.38,
      "end": 115.78,
      "text": "아, 근데 어쩔 수 없는 거잖아요."
    },
    {
